<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="flex flex-col items-center bg-[#f0f0f0] p-[2rem]">
    <div class="flex flex-col bg-[#fafafa] w-screen max-w-[600px] p-[2rem]">
      <img
        class="w-fill"
        src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1125453534062719016/1162302877507784704/Banner_Ticket.png?ex=653b71e8&is=6528fce8&hm=b97686cec57f00ef08a7b30985c857004429ae330f7fa8b19e53a57afd92992a&" />

      <div class="text-[1.2rem]">Hi <%= nama %></div>
      <div class="mt-[1rem]">Selamat pembelian tiket anda telah berhasil</div>
      <div>
        Silahkan unduh tiket untuk
        <b>HIMALAYA: Awarding Night Mr. & Ms. UMN 2023</b>
        pada lampiran email ini
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[2rem]">
        Jangan lupa untuk hadir pada waktu dan tanggal berikut:
      </div>
      <div class="flex">
        <div>
          <div>Waktu Open Gate</div>
          <div>Tanggal</div>
          <div>Tempat</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-[1rem] font-bold">
          <div>: 16.00 - 18.00 WIB</div>
          <div>: 24 November 2023</div>
          <div>: QBIG Convention Hall</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#fff0a1] p-[1rem] mt-[2rem]">
        <div class="font-bold">Tips:</div>
        <div>
          Unduh tiketmu pada lampiran email ini sebelum datang dan menghadari
          acara HIMALAYA: Awarding Night Mr. & Ms. UMN 2023.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="font-bold mt-[2rem]">Rincian Item</div>
      <div class="flex">
        <div>
          <div>No Pesanan</div>
          <div>Pesanan</div>
          <div>Jumlah Tiket</div>
          <div>Nama Pemesan</div>
          <div>No. Telephone</div>
          <div>Email</div>
        </div>

        <div class="pl-[1rem] font-bold">
          <div>: <%= transaction_id %></div>
          <div>: HIMALAYA: Awarding Night Mr. & Ms. UMN 2023</div>
          <div>: <%= jumlah_ticket %></div>
          <div>: <%= nama %></div>
          <div>: <%= wa %></div>
          <div>: <%= email %></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[2rem] flex justify-center items-center font-bold">
        <button
          href="https://mrms.umn.ac.id/e-ticket?id=<%= transaction_id %>"
          class="bg-[#fff0a1] p-[1rem] rounded-[1rem]">
          Lihat E-Tiket Anda
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col mt-[2rem] p-[1rem] w-screen max-w-[600px] bg-[#fafafa]">
      <div class="font-bold">Butuh Bantuan?</div>
      <a
        href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSedPpIfUO3BUyl6p7Cn-CzQqyBzqrSDnfpSbLhzl2HPrN4OaQ/viewform"
        ><div>Form Kendala Tiket Himalaya</div></a
      >
    </div>
    <div class="mt-[2rem] flex flex-col items-center">
      <img
        class="w-[5rem]"
        src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1062052561068228688/1065503219209478184/Logo_Mr___Ms_UMN_2023_-_Circle_copy.png?ex=6539f933&is=65278433&hm=c8b2e66028ddf0407cdad16f335eddbca1c1b3b8006c59232c5abb6f49f2bb27&" />
      <a href="https://mrms.umn.ac.id/ticket-himalaya"
        ><div class="font-bold">https://mrms.umn.ac.id/ticket-himalaya</div></a
      >
      <div>Copyright â’¸ 2023 Mr. & Ms. UMN. All rights reserved</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
